main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Baltimore, Maryland on September 16, 1965, involving probable aerial craft resembling balloons or lighted objects.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for approximately 30 minutes,The objects exhibited erratic behavior during the observation,There were no photographs or physical evidence to support the sighting,The objects were first seen moving slowly before demonstrating high speed, The sighting was reported to the Weather service by the witness.
sighted object: probable aerial craft resembling balloons or lighted objects
